<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3 style="margin:0">Setup</h3>
            <ul style="margin:0">
                <li>Set water carrier to -10</li>
                <li>Jungle draw pile with 2 tiles on display</li>
                <li>Private draw piles; hand of 3</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Add Jungle tile when adjacent to 2+ worker tiles</li>
                <li>End game trigger: some plays final worker tile</li>
                <li>Tie breaker: cacao fruit</li>
                <li>Temple Ties
                    <ul>
                        <li>1st: split top prize evenly (round down), no 2nd place rewards</li>
                        <li>2nd place: split lower prize evenly (round down)</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Overbuild
                    <ul>
                        <li>only allowed when jungle tiles have been depleted</li>
                        <li>max 1 overbuild per tile</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<h3 style="margin-bottom:0">Tile Distribution</h3>
<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4 style="margin:0">Worker Tiles</h4>
            <ul style="margin-top:0">
                <li>(4) 1-1-1-1</li>
                <li>(5) 2-1-0-1</li>
                <li>(1) 3-0-0-1</li>
                <li>(1) 3-1-0-0</li>
                <br />
                <li>(1) 0-0-2-2</li>
                <li>(1) 0-2-0-2</li>
