            <h4 style="margin:0">Jungle Tiles</h4>
            <ul style="margin-top:0">
                <li>6 <span class="cross"></span> Single plantation</li>
                <li>2 <span class="cross"></span> Double plantation</li>
                <li>2 <span class="cross"></span> Market ($2)</li>
